epub-search
===========

This is version 0.1 of epub-search. epub-search is an ePub content searching
program.

epub-search is released under the GNU General Public License (GPL) version 2,
see the file 'COPYING' for more information.


Installing
-----------

epub-search can be installed....

::

    git clone https://github.com/gregier/epub-search
    cd epub-search
    python setup.py install


Development and bug report
--------------------------

The source code is hosted on github. You can see it here:

    https://github.com/gregier/epub-search
